      "acceptanceCriteria": "Documented simulation workflow with independent peer review of model setup, boundary conditions, and post-processing scripts.",
      "rationale": "A two-analyst independent review protocol was applied. Boundary condition definitions, contact pair assignments, and post-processing scripts were reviewed against the analysis plan. No use errors were identified. RequiredLevel 2 achieved."
