      "factorType": "Model inputs",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "requiredLevel": 3,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Material properties and geometric inputs must be traceable to measurement data; uncertainty in key inputs quantified.",
      "rationale": "Elastic modulus, yield strength, and tangent modulus for Ti-6Al-4V sourced from tensile coupon testing of production-lot material (n=5 per lot). Screw geometry derived from CMM measurements. Input uncertainty propagated via Monte Carlo (n=1000); coefficient of variation on stiffness QoI = 3.2%."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorType": "Test samples",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
