      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "requiredLevel": 3,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Quantitative comparison metric (E/uval) must be below 1.96 for all QoIs; relative error below 10%.",
      "rationale": "E/uval computed for stiffness (1.41), yield force (1.78), and force at 40 mm (1.62); all below 1.96. Maximum relative error 8.1%. Pre-established acceptance criteria met for all three QoIs. Validation is successful."
    },
