      "rationale": "The assessment team determined that thermal effects during sterilization are outside the scope of the ASTM F1717 static compression-bending COU, as the standard specifies ambient-temperature testing. Consequently, no assessment of thermomechanical solver coupling was conducted. The factor is considered inapplicable to this COU by the team's judgment; however, the formal encoding retains 'not-assessed' because the exclusion was not reviewed and approved through the project's formal scoping procedure. At modelRiskLevel 3, the absence of this assessment represents a latent credibility gap that has not been formally dispositioned."
