    "rationale": "The FEA modeling framework meets pre-established acceptance criteria for all three regulatory QoIs (E/uval < 1.96; relative error < 10%) across N=11 production-representative constructs tested at two independent laboratories. The test conditions factor achieved level (2) falls below required level (3) due to single loading rate; this gap is accepted given the quasi-static COU. Overall credibility is judged sufficient to support regulatory submission for the non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw design.",
